<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") -%>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-12">
            <div class="card shadow-lg rounded-4 p-4">
                <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>At <strong>FriendZone</strong>, your privacy matters to us. We are committed to safeguarding your personal information and being fully transparent about how we use it.</p>

                <h4 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h4>
                <p>We only collect the minimum necessary personal data to offer you a secure and personalized experience, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Full Name</li>
                    <li>Email Address</li>
                    <li>User ID</li>
                    <li>Profile Picture (optional)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Data is collected only when you sign up or log in. Users can explore profiles and posts without logging in.</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
                <p>We use your information exclusively to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Create and manage your FriendZone account</li>
                    <li>Enable interactions like posting, liking, and commenting</li>
                    <li>Enhance your social experience and content recommendations</li>
                    <li>Send essential notifications and updates</li>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>We never sell, share, or rent your data to third parties.</strong></p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h4>3. Data Security</h4>
                <p>Your data's security is our top priority. Measures we take include:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Hosting on secure servers</li>
                    <li>Encryption of sensitive information</li>
                    <li>Restricted access to authorized team members only</li>
                </ul>
                <p>While we implement strong protections, no online platform can guarantee 100% security.</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h4>4. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h4>
                <p>FriendZone uses cookies to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Remember your login and preferences</li>
                    <li>Analyze site usage for better service</li>
                    <li>Provide personalized feeds and content</li>
                </ul>
                <p>You can disable cookies through your browser, but some features may not work properly without them.</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h4>5. Your Rights</h4>
                <p>You have full control over your data. You can:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access and review the information you have provided</li>
                    <li>Request corrections or deletion of your data</li>
                    <li>Opt-out of any non-essential communications</li>
                </ul>
                <p>To manage your information, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@friendzone.com">support@friendzone.com</a>.</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h4>6. Children's Privacy</h4>
                <p>FriendZone is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from minors. If you suspect a minor’s data has been submitted, please contact us immediately.</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h4>7. Updates to This Policy</h4>
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be reflected with a new "Last Updated" date. Continued use of FriendZone means you accept the updated policy.</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h4>8. Contact Us</h4>
                <p>If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback regarding your privacy, feel free to reach us at:</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@friendzone.com">support@friendzone.com</a></p>
                <p>We are committed to making your FriendZone experience safe and enjoyable.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
